When writing tests:

* Place test files next to the module they are testing
* Name test files as `<module>.test.ts`
* Do not create `__tests__` directories
* Keep tests close to the code they test for better discoverability

Example:
- For a module `user.ts`, create `user.test.ts` in the same directory
- For a module `lib/data-loaders/plaid.ts`, create `lib/data-loaders/plaid.test.ts`
